col.caption: Honest, reliable & trust worthy; open, transparent; puts the company’s & customer’s interest in the first place; complies with Government laws, regulations & Company’s policies.

Identifies and anticipates customer needs; provides prompt and high quality services to meet and excel customer needs; develops close and effective working relationships with internal and external customers; continuously searches for ways to increase customer satisfaction level.
Forward looking; optimistic and positive; a self starter to convey a sense of urgency; to propose initiatives to attain business goals despite obstacles and oppositions.
Takes ownership of the jobs; can be counted on; consistently follows through actions in a timely manner; sheer determination to take whatever necessary to execute and accomplish goals as planned.

Works closely with others to accomplish department goals; accepts, owns and contributes to team & department decisions; works effectively with other functional teams to build collaboration and achieve corporate goals.

Sensitive to market trend; active search of best practice business cases; benchmarking industrial index and competitive information around the globe; outside in market intelligence to benefit Company’s strategic growth.

Committed to continuous improvement; leads and drives improvement projects with open mind and enthusiasm; encourages and supports staff to break through and participate in the improvement actions; identifies and implements effective processes and procedures to reduce task time, increase quality, and add value to the business.
